products.title: Wrapping Up the GRND Bundle
products.body_html:
Embrace the End, Welcome the New

As we bid farewell to another year, it's time to wrap up in style and gear up for fresh beginnings. BLK & Bold brings you the exclusive "Wrapping up the GRND Bundle" - a perfect amalgamation of our signature products to elevate your coffee experience and add a dash of sophistication to your daily grind.

What's Inside the Bundle?

  • Rise & GRND Ground Coffee (12-oz): Kickstart your day with our rich and robust ground coffee. Sourced from the finest beans, it's the perfect companion for your morning reflections and plans.

  • Rise & GRND K-Cup Pods (20-count): Convenience meets quality in these K-Cup pods. Designed for the coffee lover on-the-go, these pods are a quick way to savor our signature blend, anytime, anywhere.

  • Signature BLK & Bold Mug: Sip in style with our exclusive mug. Its sleek design is not just a treat for the eyes but also ergonomically crafted for your comfort.

  • Stylish BLK & Bold Sticker Pack: Personalize your gear with our trendy sticker pack. A perfect way to showcase your love for quality coffee and a bold lifestyle.

  • Elegant BLK & Bold Logo Lapel Pin: Add a touch of class to your attire with our sophisticated lapel pin. It's more than an accessory; it's a statement.

Celebrate with a Special Offer

Retail Price: $66.50
Special Bundle Price: $45

This curated bundle is more than just a collection of items; it's a celebration of the year past and the excitement for what's ahead. The "Wrapping up the GRND Bundle" is your companion in this journey, making each moment meaningful with a sip of excellence.

This product is excluded from any discount, promotion, or any other price reduction.

products.title: Roasted Yerba Mate Loose Leaf Herbal Tea
products.body_html:
100% Loose Leaf
Flavor profile: full-bodied, chocolate, nutty
Health benefits: Rich in antioxidants, minerals, aminos, and B vitamins

Want the energy of a cup of coffee without having to drink coffee? This might be your new go-to beverage. Yerba Mate is high in caffeine and full-bodied with nutty, chocolate flavor notes. A cup of Yerba Mate Loose Leaf Tea is perfect hot or iced on-the-go.

Try our brew recipe:
1. Pour 8 oz of 160-180° F of water over 2 tsp. of loose leaf tea.
2. Steep 4-5 minutes.
3. Enjoy as is or add your preferred sweetener.

products.title: Matcha Green Tea Powder
products.body_html:
100% Powder
Flavor Profile: Nutty, smooth, sweet, earthy, silky, buttery
Health benefits: aids digestion, fights inflammation, high in antioxidants

When green tea leaves are ground into a fine powder, it becomes the smooth, buttery, earthy Matcha. Your first sip of Matcha will combine earthiness with a subtle sweetness and silky smooth texture that feels like luxury. Not to mention, there are many great ways to enjoy a cup of Matcha Green Tea- hot, iced, as a latte, or as is.

Try our brew recipe:
1. Sift 1-2 tsp matcha into a small bowl.
2. Pour in 2 oz hot (boiling) water and whisk until fully combined and a layer of foam forms.
3. Enjoy your matcha tea straight from the bowl or cup, or add 6 oz of hot milk (or dairy substitute) for a latte. Add your preferred sweetener if you like.
